sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant RuntimeHTTP as Caikit Runtime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant RuntimeGRPC as Caikit Runtime<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant EmbMod as EmbeddingModule<br/>(in-process)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformer<br/>(PyTorch)
    participant TGISMod as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(in-process)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant PeftMod as PeftPromptTuning<br/>(in-process)
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(local PyTorch)
    participant TorchDist as Torch Distributed<br/>29550/TCP

    Note over Client,TorchDist: Flow 1: Text Embedding Inference

    Client->>RuntimeHTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>or /embeddings, /rerank, /sentence-similarity
    RuntimeHTTP->>EmbMod: dispatch to EmbeddingModule.run()
    EmbMod->>STModel: SentenceTransformerWithTruncate.encode()<br/>thread-safe tokenization
    STModel-->>EmbMod: embedding vectors (float32/float16)
    EmbMod-->>RuntimeHTTP: EmbeddingResult / RerankResult
    RuntimeHTTP-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,TorchDist: Flow 2: Remote Text Generation (TGIS)

    Client->>RuntimeGRPC: gRPC caikit.runtime.Nlp/TextGeneration<br/>or ServerStreamingTextGeneration
    RuntimeGRPC->>TGISMod: dispatch to TextGenerationTGIS.run()
    TGISMod->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationRequest<br/>TLS optional (ca_cert, client_cert configurable)
    TGIS-->>TGISMod: GenerationResponse
    TGISMod-->>RuntimeGRPC: GeneratedTextResult
    RuntimeGRPC-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,TorchDist: Flow 3: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training

    Client->>RuntimeGRPC: gRPC caikit.runtime.NlpTraining/PeftPromptTuningTrain
    RuntimeGRPC->>PeftMod: dispatch to PeftPromptTuning.train()
    PeftMod->>HFModel: Load pretrained model<br/>(CausalLM or Seq2SeqLM)
    HFModel-->>PeftMod: Model loaded
    PeftMod->>PeftMod: Initialize PEFT PromptTuningConfig<br/>+ HuggingFace Accelerate
    loop Training Epochs
        PeftMod->>HFModel: Forward pass + backprop<br/>fp16/bf16 mixed precision
        opt Multi-GPU
            PeftMod->>TorchDist: torch.distributed.elastic_launch<br/>29550/TCP rendezvous
        end
    end
    PeftMod->>PeftMod: Save prompt vectors +<br/>training metadata (JSONL)
    PeftMod-->>RuntimeGRPC: TrainingJob status
    RuntimeGRPC-->>Client: Training complete
